<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-2997] CMake should not force static CRT linking</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-2997</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When writing the CMake build, I erroneously forced ZooKeeper to link to the Windows CRT statically. Instead of setting this, we should rely on CMake&apos;s defaults, and let users override it if they choose to by configuring with&#160; setting &lt;tt&gt;CMAKE_CXX_ARGS&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Windows&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
